Main welcome text: We are pleased you have chosen our clinic for your healthcare needs. At Prometei, we strive to provide excellent care in a convenient and timely manner. That's why we offer easy online appointment scheduling.
SaveTimeForAppointment: SAVE YOUR TIME, MAKE AN APPOINTMENT WITH THE DOCTOR ONLINE!

Landing1: The founders of the pain management and rehabilitation center «PROMETEI» are: NGO «Podilskyi regional development agency», NGO of people with disabilities «Samopomich» and social enterprise of people with disabilities «System solutions».
Landing2: The rehabilitation center «Genesys & System Solution» specializes in the rehabilitation and treatment of chronic and phantom pain. Our team of professionals will provide you with an individual approach and high-quality medical care. The experience is based on Israeli, Norwegian, Swedish and American best practices.
Landing3: The center works according to the methodology of Professor Ortiz Catalan, founder and director of the Center for Bionics and Pain Research in Gothenburg (Sweden), senior researcher at the Bionics Institute in Melbourne (Australia), professor of bionics at Chalmers University of Technology in Gothenburg, who has created several biomedical innovations, including the first bionic limb.
TherapeuticApproach: Therapeutic approach to help with the experience of trauma
Myo-: Use of myo- and other forms of stimulation
SelectionOfPharmacotherapy: Selection of pharmacotherapy and pain relief methods

PrometeiDescription: Prometei is an online rehabilitation platform offering free medical support exclusively for military personnel. We help those who served to connect with healthcare professionals for recovery and wellness.
PrometeiSubDescription: Over the years, Prometei has proudly supported our heroes with care and dedication, enabling countless successful treatments.
VeteranStorieDescription: Hear direct feedback from our heroes about how Prometei platform helped with their rehabilitation.
Carassava: Prometei's dedicated staff and excellent online system made my recovery process smooth and stress-free. Forever grateful!
About Scheduling: Our platform provides veterans with the opportunity to plan meetings. Doctors, in turn, provide timely medical advice.
FreeAidDescription: All military personnel have access to our comprehensive, cost-free medical assistance, ensuring your service to our nation is honored.
SecureChatDescription: Connect with healthcare providers in a secure and confidential environment, allowing for open and honest health discussions.
WellnessTipsDescription: We provide valuable wellness tips and resources for health care and prevention.
FAQAnswers: Answers to your questions about Prometei service offerings, platform use, and how we're dedicated to serving our veteran community.
RegisterDescription: Registering is easy. Simply click on the 'Sign Up' button and fill in the required information to create an account and access our services.
ChooseDoctorDescription: Absolutely. Our platform allows you to view doctor profiles and availability, empowering you to choose the best match for your needs.
WhatServiceDescription: All online consultations, appointment scheduling, and access to a wide range of medical support are free for registered users.
IsDataSecureDescription: Data security is a priority at Prometei. We ensure your information is protected with the highest standards of confidentiality and encryption.
